body.p: The following Norsemen bought or sold real estate in Chicago during the past week:
Washington Park Club to Oscar R. Petersen: Vernon Avenue, South of 61st Street. Price: $1,425.
J. R. Poole to Christine Wiklund: 73rd Street, east of Kimbark Avenue. Price, $
C. Anderson to Carl. J. Pearson: Buckingham Place, West of Halsted Street. Price, $3,500.
C. W. Race to Charles Nelson: Glenlake Avenue, near Southport Avenue. Price, $1.
Axel Ostrand to Oscar Haugan: Carmen Avenue, west of Southport Avenue. [Price not given.]
A. Johnson to T. J. Duncan: Chicago Avenue, east of Austin Avenue. Price, $3,200.
. Swenson to John : Erie Street, west of Weed Street. Price, $1,800.
Charles J. Nelson to John Bjergast: Erie Street, east of Street [North Racine Avenue]. Price, $11,000.
F. Schenk to Niels Johnson: Hamlin Avenue, south of Indiana Street. Price, $3,750.
A. Long to Lena Jacobsen: Huron Street, corner of Lincoln Street. Price, $2,500.
C. J. Anderson to Carl C. Carlson: Third Avenue, north of Augusta Street. Price, $3,950.
O. Erickson to F. Nordstrom: Green Street, north of 58th Street. Price, $7,200.
S. M. Gunderson to Margaret : Lot 25, block 6, Gunderson & Son addition. Price, $5,200.
J. L. Bray to Carl W. Davidson: lot , Bray's subdivision, lots 15 to 17, Garfield subdivision. Price, $4,500.
